This is the README file for PerlIO::unicodeeol, a PerlIO layer for
normalizing line endings.  It requires Perl version 5.7.3 or later.

* Installation

PerlIO::unicodeeol uses the standard perl module install process:

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

